description:
Gorgeous studio available in southie 2/1, all utilities included
 Unit features -hardwood floors -tons of natural light,high ceilings, city views abound! -5 min walk to beach and dorchester heights park -updated kitchen featuring granite countertops -unit comes with fridge, microwave and hot plate (no stove) -updated bathroom -heat-electricity-hot water-wifi included in rent -laundromat right across the street -beach and parks are steps away from the apartment -close to 90/93 and the bus line is right out front of the apartment -enjoy all the restaurants, shopping and bars that are here in southie and the seaport! -month to month lease, required to move in (1st mont rent and 1 month realtor fee= $2800). 
no pets, no smoking, single occupancy only

No Pets Allowed

(RLNE3825972)
